702632f-a.title: Brooklyn: 19th Street (East) - Avenue Z
702632f-a.text:
East 19th Street, west side, from and including Ave., 2, to, but not including Jerome Ave. This is St. Mark's R.C. Parochial School.
July 9, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
